Description_lang: For the driver that wants to enjoy the scenery.Significantly decreases top speed.Increases acceleration.

description_blz.en_US:
For the driver that wants to enjoy the scenery.

Significantly decreases top speed.
Increases acceleration.

Reduce la velocidad máxima significativamente.
Aumenta la aceleración.

Aumenta a aceleração.
